title: @riot
body: I am already answer the star guardian quiz...... But I didn't get me Iron....I love the Iron so much.... When can I get it in game ? Thank you. {{champion:99}}

replies.body:
The Star Guardian Icons can take *up to* a week to be delivered to your account. Sit tight while they get sent out and if you don't have it after a week has passed, let me know. ^.^

Let me know if you have any other questions.
Thank you. I will see aft a week.
